{"tid":1940723,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［要人］法國共諜學棍Jon Solomon 聯署叫人搞鳩袁國勇 中大生反擊 聯署要求法國大調查","createTime":"2020-03-24T02:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T15:23:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af4a428342797cf456e5466b8ec4f3ab06728613","tid":1940723,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇及名譽助理教授龍振邦，日前於明報以《大流行緣起武漢 十七年教訓盡忘》撰文，其後撤回。法國尚慕蘭里昂第三大學學者蘇哲安(Jon Solomon)認為文章構成「殖民種族歧視(colonial racism)」，於網上發起聯署要求校方調查袁國勇及重新考慮其聘任等。惟蘇哲安昨再發起聯署，指《明報》報道藏頭露尾，「有刻意隱瞞事實、扭曲事實、抹黑本人之嫌」，要求《明報》更正⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n另外，有中大學生今就事件發起聯署，指蘇哲安的言論誤導，更要求就一個科學家的言論作出處分。而在親北京人士積推動 23 條立法、港人擔憂言論自由受損之際，無論他是否有意為之，做法都涉打壓異見，並認為聯署並不專業科學，助長北京對港的白色恐怖。聯署又要求法國尚慕蘭里昂第三大學就事件展開調查，及重新考慮對蘇哲安的聘任。聯署至今有逾 150 人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撤文風波-聯署指袁國勇-龍振邦文章涉殖民種族歧視-法國學者再聯署指-明報-扭曲事實-抹黑/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%A4%E6%96%87%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B6%89%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%86%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87-%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1-%E6%89%AD%E6%9B%B2%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1nQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=043da03e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%A4%E6%96%87%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B6%89%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%86%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87-%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1-%E6%89%AD%E6%9B%B2%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%2F&h=1bea1ea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撤文風波-聯署指袁國勇-龍振邦文章涉殖民種族歧視-法國學者再聯署指-明報-扭曲事實-抹黑/</a><br />\n<br />\n中大聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/president-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon?recruiter=1059760002&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fpresident-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon%3Frecruiter%3D1059760002%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition%26fbclid%3DIwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1nQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=69d24737\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/president-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon?recruiter=1059760002&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y</a>"},{"pid":"cf192823ed7b5b7481caacc35d99b4dcae64008f","tid":1940723,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"條友之前出咗篇1999論文暗插反送中運動（見英文標題）<br />\n<br />\n香港，社會鬥爭與資本主義圈地運動<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, or How Social Struggles Can Reinforce the Cartography of Capitalist Enclosure<br />\n<br />\nBy Jon Solomon<br />\n<br />\n本文作者蘇哲安（Jon Solomon）現為法國里昂第三大學中文系教授，曾於台灣與香港研究與教書，批判香港反對「《逃犯條例》修正草案」運動如何繼承了殖民－帝國現代性的問題，並指出其如何再次強化主權的劃界，在此之下，所謂「自由」下所隱含的一種本質上具有人種優越感（speciestic）的未來想像，悖反地又將自身「封鎖進資本主義社會關係的再生產所必需的那些圈封的國家或區域，遭受前所未有的奴役」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jonsolomon.academia.edu/research#papers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonsolomon.academia.edu%2Fresearch%23papers&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1nQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=628ddd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jonsolomon.academia.edu/research#papers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友又係cornell出身<br />\nCornell出過好多共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見<br />\n[所謂專家] 中美貿易戰論輸贏 權威證據：美國才是輸家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1047886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1047886</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8caae4d133ce1f79606b7ebb154b77082c155a25","tid":1940723,"uid":75982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:07:28.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"25ad91555ac232abf2ee416dad0832df496c24af","tid":1940723,"uid":246215,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:12:16.000Z","msg":"呢D蝦毛仔唔駛理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪由得佢，根本唔會有人理，中大仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c769e0b9e19fa9eea72898cd7a4dd75bb04b2bf4","tid":1940723,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"635aa918d16a372dd46e5c52fdc526ea5c52f06d","tid":1940723,"uid":246215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"on9兒登仔<br />\n知唔知呢類人最想係咩呀？係曝光率呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d3823d681b90e7a9a4078d7bafae5561ae4fa3","tid":1940723,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"Signed <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多手足需要目擊證人：</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_evidence&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1nQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=4e92351d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http